10 unit Beef Tenderloin Filets
1 unit Pepper
25 milliliters Sherry Vinegar
12 g Beef Stock Concentrate
1 unit Beef Demi-Glace
1 ounce Roasted Garlic Herb Butter
1 pound Potatoes
23 g Sour Cream
9.6 g Chicken Stock Concentrate
1 unit Garlic
2 ounce Shallot
¼ ounce Sage
¼ ounce Thyme
½ cup Flour
1 teaspoon Cinnamon
6 ounce Green Beans
½ ounce Pecans
1 tablespoon Brown Sugar
2 unit Brioche Buns
2.5 ounce Celery Sticks
2 unit Eggs
1 unit Yellow Onion
1 teaspoon Garlic Powder
9.6 g Veggie Stock Concentrate
1 ounce Dried Cranberries
1 unit Granny Smith Apple
1 unit Lemon
8 ounce Milk

1. Follow our 4-hour dinner game plan included in the comprehensive instruction booklet for a same-day Thanksgiving dinner.